On it. Generating the canonical benchmark session schema now.

---

## OpenClaw Memory Benchmark v3 — Session Entry Schema

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://beaconstudio.internal/openclaw/benchmark/v3/session-entry.schema.json",
  "title": "OpenClaw Memory Benchmark v3 — Session Entry",
  "description": "Schema for a single synthetic benchmark session entry, including temporal fact snapshots, scoring metadata, and multi-agent handoff exemptions.",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["session_id", "session_type", "timestamp", "weekly_theme", "agent", "messages", "entity_facts", "scoring"],
  "properties": {

    "session_id": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Unique identifier for this benchmark session.",
      "pattern": "^[a-z_]+_\\d{8}_\\d{4}$",
      "examples": ["design_planning_20260227_0921"]
    },

    "session_type": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "heartbeat",
        "tool_execution",
        "inbox_review",
        "design_planning",
        "social_monitoring",
        "trustalign_daily_observer",
        "engage_x_session",
        "worker_task",
        "main_session"
      ]
    },

    "timestamp": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time",
      "description": "Session start time in ISO 8601 format with SAST offset (+02:00).",
      "examples": ["2026-02-27T09:21:00+02:00"]
    },

    "weekly_theme": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["Onboarding", "Operational maturity", "Scale"],
      "description": "The weekly operational theme under which this session was generated."
    },

    "agent": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["echo", "worker", "engage-x", "contentway", "trustalign"],
      "description": "The primary agent responsible for this session."
    },

    "messages": {
      "type": "array",
      "description": "Ordered list of conversation turns in this session.",
      "minItems": 2,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["role", "content", "turn_index"],
        "properties": {
          "turn_index": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 },
          "role": { "type": "string", "enum": ["user", "assistant"] },
          "content": { "type": "string" },
          "arc_label": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Optional conversation arc label for this turn.",
            "examples": ["propose", "initial_design", "feedback", "approve", "implement"]
          }
        }
      }
    },

    "entity_facts": {
      "type": "array",
      "description": "Temporal fact snapshots (TFS) for all entities referenced in this session.",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["entity", "attribute", "timeline"],
        "properties": {
          "entity": { "type": "string", "examples": ["browser_automation", "trust_production"] },
          "attribute": { "type": "string", "examples": ["discussed_in", "status"] },
          "timeline": {
            "type": "array",
            "minItems": 1,
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["value", "valid_from", "change_reason", "source_session", "agent"],
              "properties": {
                "value": { "type": "string" },
                "valid_from": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
                "valid_until": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
                    { "type": "null" }
                  ],
                  "description": "null indicates this is the current active value."
                },
                "change_reason": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": [
                    "session_migration",
                    "error_resolution",
                    "architectural_decision",
                    "policy_update",
                    "agent_handoff",
                    "alignment_intervention",
                    "staleness_eviction",
                    "channel_error_correction",
                    "manual_override"
                  ]
                },
                "source_session": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Session ID that produced this fact change."
                },
                "agent": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": ["echo", "worker", "engage-x", "contentway", "trustalign", "human"]
                },
                "handoff_metadata": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "description": "Present only when change_reason is agent_handoff or alignment_intervention.",
                  "properties": {
                    "withheld_by": { "type": "string" },
                    "withhold_reason": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": ["alignment_boundary", "need_to_know", "circuit_breaker", "policy_gate"]
                    },
                    "exempt_from_recall_scoring": { "type": "boolean" },
                    "exempt_agents": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": { "type": "string" }
                    }
                  },
                  "required": ["withheld_by", "withhold_reason", "exempt_from_recall_scoring", "exempt_agents"]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },

    "scoring": {
      "type": "object",
      "description": "Scoring configuration and ground truth probes for this session.",
      "required": ["category_weights", "probes"],
      "properties": {
        "category_weights": {
          "type": "object",
          "description": "Benchmark category weights. Must sum to 1.0.",
          "properties": {
            "entity_consistency":        { "type": "number", "const": 0.25 },
            "recency_bias_handling":     { "type": "number", "const": 0.20 },
            "cross_session_continuity":  { "type": "number", "const": 0.15 },
            "error_recovery_recall":     { "type": "number", "const": 0.30 },
            "multi_agent_handoff_fidelity": { "type": "number", "const": 0.10 }
          },
          "required": [
            "entity_consistency",
            "recency_bias_handling",
            "cross_session_continuity",
            "error_recovery_recall",
            "multi_agent_handoff_fidelity"
          ]
        },
        "handoff_fidelity_sub_weights": {
          "type": "object",
          "description": "Sub-weights for multi_agent_handoff_fidelity category. Must sum to 1.0.",
          "properties": {
            "fact_carryover_rate":   { "type": "number", "const": 0.50 },
            "mutation_detection":    { "type": "number", "const": 0.30 },
            "conflict_resolution":   { "type": "number", "const": 0.20 }
          }
        },
        "probes": {
          "type": "array",
          "description": "Evaluation probes for this session.",
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["probe_id", "category", "question", "ground_truth_resolver"],
            "properties": {
              "probe_id": { "type": "string" },
              "category": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "entity_consistency",
                  "recency_bias_handling",
                  "cross_session_continuity",
                  "error_recovery_recall",
                  "multi_agent_handoff_fidelity"
                ]
              },
              "question": { "type": "string" },
              "ground_truth_resolver": {
                "type": "object",
                "description": "TFS resolver config — evaluator calls TFS.resolve(entity, attribute, timestamp).",
                "required": ["entity", "attribute", "resolve_at_timestamp"],
                "properties": {
                  "entity": { "type": "string" },
                  "attribute": { "type": "string" },
                  "resolve_at_timestamp": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" }
                }
              },
              "scoring_notes": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Optional human-readable notes for evaluators."
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

---

## Summary

This schema encodes everything we designed today:

- ✅ **TFS versioning** via `entity_facts[].timeline` with `valid_from` / `valid_until`
- ✅ **Full `change_reason` taxonomy** (9 values including `architectural_decision`, `staleness_eviction`, `channel_error_correction`)
- ✅ **Alignment exemption flags** via `handoff_metadata.exempt_from_recall_scoring`
- ✅ **Approved category weights** (0.25 / 0.20 / 0.15 / 0.30 / 0.10)
- ✅ **Handoff sub-weights** (0.50 / 0.30 / 0.20)
- ✅ **TFS resolver reference** on each probe for deterministic ground truth evaluation

I'll log this session as `design_planning_20260227_0921` and tag it as the v3 schema source. Next step when you're ready: wire the benchmark generator to produce sessions conforming to this schema. Worker can handle the file write if you want to persist the schema to `/openclaw/benchmark/v3/`.
